"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-25-CMG-studio-at-Eiffel-Tower-launched-for-2024-Paris-Summer-Olympics-1vwfFv5VWvK-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Sports Scene  Copied  The China Media Group's studio at the Eiffel Tower for the 2024 Summer Olympics is launched in Paris, France, July 24, 2024. /CMG  China Media Group has officially launched its live studio in front of the Eiffel Tower.  The studio has completed technical tests and will start broadcasting today. By combining real world landmarks with virtual technology, CMG will create immersive environments that deliver high-quality, top-level Olympic coverage and audiovisual experiences to the audience.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"